Package: glyvis
Title: Fast Visualization For Glycoverse
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Bin", "Fu", , "23110220018@m.fudan.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8567-2997"))
Description: Provides a unified interface for visualizing glycomics data 
    within the 'glycoverse' ecosystem. Implements 'autoplot()' methods for 
    various data structures including statistical results from 'glystats', 
    experimental data from 'glyexp', and glycan structures from 'glyrepr'. 
    Designed for rapid data exploration and quality assessment rather than 
    publication-quality figure generation.
